    {
      "id": 17,
      "title": "Alert Rules Reference",
      "description": "Summary of all alert rules for the Mitigation Measure Designer agent with conditions, severity, and notification channels.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 59 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## EUDR-029 Mitigation Measure Designer Alert Rules\n\n| # | Alert | Condition | Severity | Evaluation | Action |\n|---|-------|-----------|----------|------------|--------|\n| 1 | **Overdue Measures** | gl_eudr_mmd_overdue_measures > 0 for 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 15m | Review overdue measures, escalate to compliance lead |\n| 2 | **Critical Overdue** | gl_eudr_mmd_overdue_measures > 10 for 30m | Critical | Every 5m, for 5m | Page on-call, activate emergency response |\n| 3 | **Approval Bottleneck** | gl_eudr_mmd_pending_approvals > 20 for 4h | Warning | Every 15m, for 1h | Review approval queue, notify approvers |\n| 4 | **Low Effectiveness** | gl_eudr_mmd_avg_risk_reduction < 15% after 90 days | Warning | Every 1h, for 24h | Review strategy design, consider template updates |\n| 5 | **High API Error Rate** | API 5xx error rate > 1% for 5 minutes | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, check infrastructure |\n| 6 | **Strategy Design Latency** | p99 > 5s for 10 minutes | Warning | Every 5m, for 10m | Investigate performance, check database queries |\n\n### Notification Channels\n- **Critical**: PagerDuty + Slack #eudr-critical + Email compliance-lead\n- **Warning**: Slack #eudr-alerts + Email on-call\n\n### Runbook Links\n- [Overdue Measures Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/overdue-measures)\n- [Approval Bottleneck Resolution](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/approval-bottleneck)\n- [Low Effectiveness Investigation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/low-effectiveness)\n- [Strategy Design Troubleshooting](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/strategy-design)\n- [Verification Failures](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/verification-failures)\n- [Performance Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/mmd/perf-degradation)"
      }
    }
  ],
